    <main>
      <h2>sunday morning</h2>
      
      <div class="content">
	<p>
	  forgetting my training
	</p>

	<p>
	  I have allowed myself to be pulled to and fro
	<br>
	  by the changing winds of aversion and desire blown in rings in my face
	<br>
	  and blackening my lungs with lust for things not needed and fear of things not present
	</p>
	<p>
	  I have become arrogant to expect my will be carried out without exception
	<br>
	  while the vision of the setting moon in the kitchen window is still there
	<br>
	and guides me where I need to go;
	</p>
	<p>
	  if you look closely<br>
	  with patience<br>
	  you will see it move
	</p>
      </div>
      

    
